---
title: "US11 — Create / update fitness profile"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>FitnessProfileScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>UpsertFitnessProfile
  participant G as «Gateway»<br/>FitnessGateway → Supabase
  A->>B: edit metrics, chips, tags - tap SAVE PROFILE
  B->>C: save(patch)
  C->>G: update fitness_profiles (one batched write)
  G-->>C: ok / error
  alt saved
    C-->>B: refreshed profile
    B-->>A: "Fitness profile saved."
  else write fails
    C-->>B: AsyncError
    B-->>A: "Could not save. Please try again."
  end
